webpackJsonp([45016050039385],{4876:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Mainstream",date:"24 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-24-mainstream/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>You know blogging has become mainstream when the <a href="http://www.startribune.com/509/story/1203387.html">closing down of a blog</a> hits a major daily newspaper.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.bat-girl.com/">Batgirl</a> was a somewhat different sports blog with "less stats, more sass". <a href="http://www.bat-girl.com/archives/001883.php">I\'ll miss it.</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Alternative Sentencing",date:"24 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-24-alternative-sentencing/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Karen King McDonald's Ad",date:"25 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-25-karen-king-mcdonalds-ad/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Alternative Sentencing",date:"24 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-24-alternative-sentencing/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>Does the sentence fit the crime?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>In Hildesheim, the founder of Heros, once Germany\'s leading money transport company, was <a href="http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2007/05/23/business/EU-FIN-Germany-Embezzlement-Trial.php">convicted</a> (along with 3 managers) of <a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2006/02/20/if-you-cant-trust-your-armored-car-company/">embezzling half a billion Euros</a> over 2 decades, and was sentenced to 10 years in prison.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>In Atanta, a former secretary for Coca-Cola was <a href="http://www.businessweek.com/ap/financialnews/D8PA8HM80.htm">convicted of conspiring to sell trade secrets</a> to Pepsi for $1.5 million, and was sentenced to 8 years in prison (longer than was recommended by the prosecution).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>'},next:{fields:{title:"Bergedorf",date:"23 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-23-bergedorf/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Mainstream",date:"24 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-24-mainstream/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Bergedorf",date:"23 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-23-bergedorf/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/510374606/"><img src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2007/05/bergedorf-mcdonalds-1991.jpg" alt="bergedorf mcdonalds 1991" /></a></p>\n<p>"At the McDrive a dream came true": Newspaper article on the opening of McDrive restaurant in Hamburg-Bergedorf, 1991</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Uptown",date:"22 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-22-uptown/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Alternative Sentencing",date:"24 May 2007",slug:"/2007-05-24-alternative-sentencing/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:125,pageCount:1101}}}});
